window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Son of the shaman is a shaman - but what of the daughters?</b></p> <p>When Otto Krugg's daughter follows in his footsteps, he's faced with the task of changing a century-long rule that will force her to make decisions no one should have to make.</p> <p>When Jimmy Pirano gets tasked with enforcing that rule - no matter what - he goes down the rabbit hole to try to find out who established the rule...and why they can't let it go.</p>"; 
